{"tid":1857641,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"深圳首次發現新型肺炎社區傳播病例 其中一人從事外賣","createTime":"2020-02-02T09:29:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-02T10:00:34.000Z","uid":125193,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"ce41c75a937460b072ed596d134de9850ff84299","tid":1857641,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T09:29:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1506208-20200202.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1506208-20200202.htm&d=m5PK5j%2F1EvBSK5XTwnZL9Ga%2FpyP0knsd4enDGc0qzPM%3D&h=8621f469\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1506208-20200202.htm&h=4c9aa54b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1506208-20200202.htm</a>"},{"pid":"1558c55de9ede3a9d3b6535f18de89676e374b4b","tid":1857641,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T09:30:24.000Z","msg":"深圳市首次發現社區傳播病例，有3名患者在病發前14日，都無離開過深圳，其中一名患者，在深圳從事送外賣工作。<br />\n<br />\n深圳市疾控中心副主任醫師孔東鋒表示，3名患者可能在公共日常交往過程中，在不知情下接觸到傳染病源，呼籲市民外出時，一定要佩戴口罩，接觸公共物品後要勤洗手，避免聚會和減少到人多不通風的場所。<br />\n<br />\n廣東省截至中午，累計新型冠狀病毒感染肺炎確診病例為632宗，28宗新增確診個案。廣東省衛健委副主任陳祝生表示，疫情防控十分嚴峻，確診病例數目，仍在上升階段，暫時病例以湖北及相關地區輸入為主，但隨著假期結束，回廣東人數增加，疫情防控進入關鍵時期。"},{"pid":"0e60dfd840e81de443f322985faf99d2da16e0e1","tid":1857641,"uid":58552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T09:30:43.000Z","msg":"屌"},{"pid":"f09e2f4fe85da2aadc9a247797dd13baa3c5ed9e","tid":1857641,"uid":169195,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"ce41c75a937460b072ed596d134de9850ff84299","tid":1857641,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T09:29:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1506208-20200202.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1506208-20200202.htm&d=m5PK5